  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/efd7600405fe91c69433363e0be96a53.poster.avif?t=1773806955\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/efd7600405fe91c69433363e0be96a53.webm?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/efd7600405fe91c69433363e0be96a53.mp4?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Naval Armada is a Sea battle for survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captain, the sea is challenging you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead exciting MMORPG naval battles online, choose warships and control them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends against enemies and win epic battles of destroyers, cruisers and battleships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/3020f39f020d9cbce5bf5e2e87ef3d23.poster.avif?t=1773806955\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/3020f39f020d9cbce5bf5e2e87ef3d23.webm?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/3020f39f020d9cbce5bf5e2e87ef3d23.mp4?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your fighting style! Crazy battles in free mode or planned attacks in group battles?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your ship into a real death machine! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accept the Naval battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/057e2b2ea23a1001ce621dd75368c201.poster.avif?t=1773806955\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/057e2b2ea23a1001ce621dd75368c201.webm?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/057e2b2ea23a1001ce621dd75368c201.mp4?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Lots warships! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Different classes of ships and different weapons. From light guns, to torpedoes and missiles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Unique upgrade system for each ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Many battle arenas from different parts of the world are waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Modern 3D graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Intuitive operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show your opponents what warships are capable of under the control of an experienced commander! The war will judge who is right!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who are you? An ordinary captain out of thousands, or the one who is feared?  You won't know until you take the fight...</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/efd7600405fe91c69433363e0be96a53.poster.avif?t=1773806955\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/efd7600405fe91c69433363e0be96a53.webm?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/efd7600405fe91c69433363e0be96a53.mp4?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Naval Armada is a Sea battle for survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captain, the sea is challenging you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead exciting MMORPG naval battles online, choose warships and control them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends against enemies and win epic battles of destroyers, cruisers and battleships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/3020f39f020d9cbce5bf5e2e87ef3d23.poster.avif?t=1773806955\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/3020f39f020d9cbce5bf5e2e87ef3d23.webm?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/618620/extras/3020f39f020d9cbce5bf5e2e87ef3d23.mp4?t=1773806955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your fighting style! Crazy battles in free mode or planned attacks in group battles?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your ship into a real death machine! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accept the Naval battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video 